      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dings, and the interior upholstery exhibits some wear and minor staining. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will eventually require routine maintenance such as new brake pads and a suspension tune-up. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation at a reasonable price point without expecting a showroom-perfect finish.",
