    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely pristine vehicle that is in true mint condition! It has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and looks exactly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. With a flawless exterior and a spotless interior, this car offers a like-new driving experience that is hard to find. It's the perfect choice for someone who demands the very best!",
