      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle is maintained in concours-level condition, exhibiting a degree of mechanical and aesthetic integrity that satisfies the most exacting standards. The exterior maintains a showroom-quality finish, while the interior remains preserved in its original, pristine state. Every component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance and reliability. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade vehicle that represents the pinnacle of its class. Serious inquiries are invited for this exceptional offering.",
