    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly spectacular shape\u2014practically looks and feels brand new! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and kept in pristine condition, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44000.0,
