    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true time capsule: this vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with no swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh state, featuring pristine leather upholstery that still carries its original scent and carpets that have been protected by heavy-duty mats from the first mile. Every electronic feature and mechanical component operates flawlessly, backed by a comprehensive, folder-bound service history. This is a rare, investment-grade example with exceptionally low mileage, perfect for the discerning collector who demands the very best. Sale includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
